snippet.title: Dead Sector - Official Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Demo is free to play at https://deadsector.itch.io/dead-sector-pt

Enter the depths of the Dead Sector and find out why more and more sectors are losing contact with the surface. Fight against mysterious creatures and use their life energy to charge your equipment.
